<p><strong>Quick practice sentence:</strong> 她的眼睛很大，鼻子很小。(Tā de yǎnjing hěn dà, bízi hěn xiǎo.) — Her eyes are big, and her nose is small.</p>

<h2 id="upper-body">Upper Body (上半身)</h2>

<p>The upper body includes your torso, arms, and hands. Notice how many of these characters share the <strong>月 (flesh)</strong> radical — we'll explore this pattern in detail below.</p>

