<div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a); padding:1.25rem; border-radius:12px; margin:1.5rem 0;">
  <p style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">💡 大 vs 小 Pattern</p>
  <p style="margin:0;">Chinese uses 大 (big) and 小 (small) to distinguish upper and lower parts: <strong>大腿</strong> = thigh (big leg), <strong>小腿</strong> = calf (small leg). This same pattern appears in other areas too.</p>
