<h2 id="internal-organs">Internal Organs (内脏)</h2>

<p>You don't need to memorize every organ, but knowing the key ones helps with health discussions, <a href="/chinese/blog/chinese-food-vocabulary/">food vocabulary</a> (some are eaten!), and understanding common expressions.</p>

<table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin:1.5rem 0;">
