    <tr><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">腰疼 (yāo téng)</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">lower back pain</td></tr>
    <tr style="background:#fef2f2;"><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">膝盖疼 (xīgài téng)</td><td style="padding:8px; border:1px solid #e2e8f0;">knee pain</td></tr>
  </tbody>
